---
title: "Can AI See Me? — The story of the deliberation"
description: "A story-first reading of the “Can AI See Me?” Pol.is deliberation: what a room of faith leaders, peacebuilders, and technologists agreed on, how its opinions actually organize, and what it asked of AI governance."
---

